race.comment: GALWAY FLYER (3) drifted back early on debut when a respectable fourth over 1300m at Hawkesbury. Strips fitter and will keep improving as he gets out in trip. STRASSMAN (6) trained on the track and indicated he was near his top when a tidy second over 1400m at the Sapphire Coast. Up in class and assess on his good third over the 1300m her last prep. Will be doing his best work late. VASALA (7) four-year-old Snitzel gelding out of Dashoff on debut for the Waterhouse & Bott yard. Given the four recent trials and expected to figure prominently. AUDENZIA (8) resumes after running some respectable minor placings at this track last campaign. Fitted with the one 780m trial and shapes as the leading player.
